{"tid":166792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登仔拍住上]爭取廿三條有得傾,全登力撐薯片!","createTime":"2017-03-22T11:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T11:00:58.000Z","uid":49388,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f562f9961834bd22b07557e7b0195603a5bd8b6","tid":166792,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:32:32.000Z","msg":"今次泛民與薯片作政治上的交易妥協是為换取更大的政治商討空間,當中包括雙方能就基本法廿三條立法坐底商議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊傾一齊砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n方能化解社會分歧,砌出符合港人意願的廿三條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n這就是以政治交易換來的政治實利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n單是廿三條有得傾已是回歸20來最大的民主進步,亦是03年50萬人上街及佔鐘時與暴力行動劃清界線的實質成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相反林鄭必定一意孤行,不作討論,自把自為地為廿三條立法,社會便急速撕裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外,候選人性格外型亦是投票意願重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n奶媽林鄭機心重,乞人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />常反白眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />相反薯片為人善良,純良,隨和,笑容多,容易相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />亦能將香港形象大大提升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />是香港精神的代表人物,他的當選必能修復港人與中央祖國的分歧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天,我們連登巴打就與曾俊華拍住上!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為港人為我們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />信任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />john曾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc7bbc73e1d282d1c3bf7f6a272bc7c31598840","tid":166792,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T